<h2 id="due_diligence">Due Diligence</h2>

<p>
The first step to finding stuff on CPAN is to try to use the
<a href="http://metacpan.org/"><b>MetaCPAN</b></a> search engine, which
has many measures for facilitating finding high quality stuff, including
upvotes, ratings, comments, links to bug trackers, and many more.
</p>
